[('Laid out and desperate
 No blood here left to bleed', [['Repetition of the phrase, “laid out and desperate” and similar blood loss imagery is found in the 5th track, “Desperate.”

“Every day and night;
we’re laid out and desperate
Every day and night;
we’re bloodied and broken”']]), ('With the moon shining down on me', [['The phrase “moon shining down” is repeated in the 8th track, “Dealer / Debtor”.']])]
